		<title>16Religion and social concerns</title>
		<content>                                       
     Attendance at our six places of   
 worship is in decline.We have a church
 and five chapels.One Gosen closed     
 in 1983 due to lack of membership.    
     The Community Council run a Day   
 Centre for the elderly twice a week.A 
 street Warden scheme for the disabled 
 and elderly is at present being       
 discussed.An increase in one parent   
 families has occured over the last    
 five years.This is something quite new
 because the family group or unit is a 
 characteristic of this area.          
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
